body.name: Belkin 6-Outlet Surge Protector Power Strip, Wall-Mountable with 6 AC Outlets, Overvoltage Protection, LED Indicator - USB-C Port & USB-A Port w/USB-C PD Fast Charging - 1680 Joules of Protection
body.merchantInfo: Sold by Amazon Warehouse and Fulfilled by Amazon.
features: MULTI-OUTLET SURGE PROTECTOR POWER STRIP: Turn 1 outlet into 6 surge-protected AC outlets wrapped in a slim and modern design. Power multiple computing devices and peripherals, from iPhones, tablets, and smartphones to laptops and projectors.

SAFEGUARD YOUR DEVICES & APPLIANCES: Secure your devices with 1680 joules of overcurrent and overload protection; designed with hardworking MOVs to protect the life of your computers, monitors, hard drives, home theaters and other appliances.

USB-C & USB-A PORTS: Safely charge your personal devices with this versatile wall surge protector. One powered USB-C PD port and 1 USB-A port provide convenient, one-source charging for your mobile devices, including smartphones and tablets.

SAFETY LIGHT INDICATOR: This wall mount surge protector features a safety indicator light to put your mind at ease while charging. The protected indicator light lets you know your equipment is secure or if your outlet needs to be readjusted.
UL SAFETY CERTIFIED: This product has been independently lab tested and certified to meet or exceed UL safety standards.

RELIABLE SURGE PROTECTOR: An updated, smarter design includes safety features to minimize electrical power risks. And you can purchase with confidence as it is backed by a 2-year limited lifetime warranty and $25,000 Connected Equipment Warranty.
body.description: Protect the life of your electronics and minimize electrical power risks with this Belkin surge protector, featuring 6 AC outlets and added USB-C and USB-A ports. Upgrade to a new Belkin protector to plug in electronics and appliances at home with confidence in 1680 joules of surge protection and the latest safety features. This surge protector power strip allows 22.5W charging through your USB-C PD port, and you can access the commonly used USB-A PD port for even more flexibility. Built-in mounts free up space if you opt to place it on your wall, and our 2-year warranty gives you peace of mind with a best-in-class Connected Equipment Warranty of up to $25,000.Belkin is an established accessories market leader creating high-quality, innovative tech solutions for 40 years.Specifications:Electrical Rating: 1875WMax Voltage: 15A/125VSurge Protection: 1680JCompatibility: Compatible with AC outlets, plus most AC, USB-C PD, and USB-A compatible devicesUL-compliant2-year limited warranty, Connected Equipment Warranty of up to $25,000.This product is made with a minimum of 72% post-consumer recycled content, and 100% plastic free packaging.
